{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8a2b4c10-5f6e-4d3a-9b21-ifreeicloud0001",
    "name": "iFreeiCloud API",
    "description": "Manual exploration of the iFreeiCloud API (https://api.ifreeicloud.co.uk).\n\nAll requests are POST against a single host. The body discriminates the operation:\n- `service=<id>` → run an instant service\n- `accountinfo=servicelist` → list services\n- `accountinfo=balance` → account balance\n\nSet the collection variables (or import the matching environment file) before sending:\n- `baseUrl` — defaults to `https://api.ifreeicloud.co.uk`\n- `apiKey`  — your iFreeiCloud API key (XXX-XXX-XXX-XXX-XXX-XXX-XXX-XXX)\n- `imei`    — IMEI/serial to test against\n\nFor SDK usage see https://www.npmjs.com/package/@hopla/ifreeicloud.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "https://api.ifreeicloud.co.uk", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "apiKey", "value": "YOUR_API_KEY_HERE", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "imei", "value": "354442067957123", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Collection-wide post-response checks",
          "pm.test('HTTP 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
          "const data = pm.response.json();",
          "pm.test('envelope shape', () => {",
          "  pm.expect(data).to.have.property('success');",
          "});",
          "if (data.success !== true) {",
          "  console.warn('iFreeiCloud error:', data.error);",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Account",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Balance",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "accountinfo", "value": "balance", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "key", "value": "{{apiKey}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] },
            "description": "Returns the account balance in `object.account_balance` (USD)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Service List",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "accountinfo", "value": "servicelist", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "key", "value": "{{apiKey}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] },
            "description": "Returns the live catalog of instant services. `response` is HTML, `object` is keyed by service ID with name/price/time/description/snSupport/objectSupport."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
